72621D3E.Line11.E2C66: Go to his shrine. Honor him there. Perhaps he will commune with Túr Dúlra's savior.

91402C31.Line5.E2C66: They don’t listen when we call back. Their pain...

C5291F35.Line9.E2C66: There is one who might help. The spirit Gathlen. He's a healer of his kind. (pained groan) Or he was, until the college fell.

F74BB2AF.Line3.E2C66: You’ve healed this place, but the spirits here still ache with rot. It was their cries you heard.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “Túr Dúlra called out to me in pain.”
